Celebi (TCG)

From Bulbapedia, the community-driven Pokémon encyclopedia.
Jump to navigationJump to search
← #0250: Ho-Oh
Pokémon
#0252: Treecko →
For Pokémon TCG Pocket cards, see Celebi (TCG Pocket).

Celebi has been featured on 34 different cards since it debuted in the Neo Revelation expansion of the Pokémon Trading Card Game. Celebi cards are normally Grass-type or Psychic-type Basic Pokémon.

List of Pokémon cards featuring Celebi

Celebi
Cards listed with a blue background are only legal to use in the current Expanded format.
Cards listed with a green background are legal to use in both the current Standard and Expanded formats.
